N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 133.14 - Service of Papers

State Regulations

All notices and papers connected with a hearing, other than
the notice of hearing, may be served by electronic mail or regular first class
mail, unless otherwise stated. Except where otherwise provided, service by
regular first class mail shall be deemed complete five (5) calendar days after
mailing. Notes
